title: Passengers warned to check before travel after airport closes
text:
Passengers are being advised to check before travelling after a security alert forced the closure of Humberside airport.
Humberside airport Credit: Anna Gowthorpe/PA Archive/PA Images Police say they were called in this morning after a "suspicious package" was found in a vehicle parked in an airport car park.
A18 is closed from the Melton Ross Bridge and Kirmington crossroads.
For the latest travel information travellers are being urged to contact airlines or tour operators.
